					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">2000 military operation in Sierra Leone led by the United Kingdom</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<table class="infobox vevent" style="width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;"><tbody><tr><th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Operation Barras</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;">Part of the <a href="/wiki/Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" title="Sierra Leone Civil War">Sierra Leone Civil War</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;line-height:1.5em;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:UNsierraleone.PNG" class="mw-file-description"><img alt="Map of Sierra Leone" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/UNsierraleone.PNG/260px-UNsierraleone.PNG" decoding="async" width="260" height="328" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/UNsierraleone.PNG/390px-UNsierraleone.PNG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/UNsierraleone.PNG/520px-UNsierraleone.PNG 2x" data-file-width="2293" data-file-height="2895" /></a></span><br />A map of Sierra Leone on which is marked <a href="/wiki/Freetown" title="Freetown">Freetown</a> (the capital, to the extreme west) and the nearby towns of <a href="/wiki/Hastings,_Sierra_Leone" title="Hastings, Sierra Leone">Hastings</a> (where the SAS and Paras prepared for the operation) and <a href="/wiki/Masiaka" title="Masiaka">Masiaka</a> (where the Jordanian detachment of UNAMSIL was based)</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2"><table style="width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0;display:inline-table"><tbody><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Date</th><td>10 September 2000</td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Location</th><td><div class="location">Occra Hills, <a href="/wiki/Sierra_Leone" title="Sierra Leone">Sierra Leone</a><br /><span class="geo-inline"><span class="plainlinks nourlexpansion load-gadget" data-gadget="WikiMiniAtlas"><a class="external text" href="https://geohack.toolforge.org/geohack.php?pagename=Operation_Barras&amp;params=8.556_N_12.797_W_type:city"><span class="geo-default"><span class="geo-dms" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location"><span class="latitude">8°33′22″N</span> <span class="longitude">12°47′49″W</span></span></span><span class="geo-multi-punct">&#xfeff; / &#xfeff;</span><span class="geo-nondefault"><span class="geo-dec" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location">8.556°N 12.797°W</span><span style="display:none">&#xfeff; / <span class="geo">8.556; -12.797</span></span></span></a></span></span></div></td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Result</th><td class="status">
British victory, all hostages rescued.</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Belligerents</th></tr><tr><td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
United Kingdom</td><td style="width:50%;padding-left:0.25em">
<a href="/wiki/West_Side_Boys" title="West Side Boys">West Side Boys</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Commanders and leaders</th></tr><tr><td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
<a href="/wiki/John_Holmes_(British_Army_officer)" title="John Holmes (British Army officer)">John Holmes</a></td><td style="width:50%;padding-left:0.25em">
Foday Kallay&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prisoner_of_war" title="Prisoner of war"><abbr title="Prisoner of war">POW</abbr></a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Strength</th></tr><tr><td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
150<sup id="cite_ref-Fowler_04_126_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Fowler_04_126-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td><td style="width:50%;padding-left:0.25em">
100–200<sup id="cite_ref-Fowler_04_126_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Fowler_04_126-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Connaughton_110_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Connaughton_110-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Casualties and losses</th></tr><tr><td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
1 killed<br />12 wounded<sup id="cite_ref-fifty_eight_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-fifty_eight-3">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td><td style="width:50%;padding-left:0.25em">
25+ killed<br />18 captured<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>
<div class="navbox-styles"></div><div role="navigation" class="navbox" aria-labelledby="Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" style="margin:0;float:right;clear:right;width:25.5em;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-left:1em;;padding:3px"><table class="nowraplinks navbox-vertical mw-collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner" style="border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit"><tbody><tr><th scope="col" class="navbox-title" colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;"><div class="navbar plainlinks hlist navbar-mini"><ul><li class="nv-view"><a href="/wiki/Template:Campaignbox_Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" title="Template:Campaignbox Sierra Leone Civil War"><abbr title="View this template" style=";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">v</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-talk"><a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Campaignbox_Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" title="Template talk:Campaignbox Sierra Leone Civil War"><abbr title="Discuss this template" style=";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a href="/wiki/Special:EditPage/Template:Campaignbox_Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" title="Special:EditPage/Template:Campaignbox Sierra Leone Civil War"><abbr title="Edit this template" style=";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id="Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><span style="line-height:1.6em"><a href="/wiki/Sierra_Leone_Civil_War" title="Sierra Leone Civil War"><span class="wrap">Sierra Leone Civil War</span></a></span></div></th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Operation_Silver_Anvil" title="Operation Silver Anvil"><i>Silver Anvil</i></a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/1992_Sierra_Leonean_coup_d%27%C3%A9tat" title="1992 Sierra Leonean coup d&#39;état">1992 coup</a></li>
